These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-1::.
There 4 different types of food: orange, cabbage, kale, peach
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, disco, country, salsa
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hedgehog, fish, ferret
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, subway, boat, helicopter
 1. the person driving the subway is the fan of disco##1
 2. the person eating kale is the fan of country##1
 3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the fan of soul##1
 5. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the fan of disco##1
 6. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 7. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
 8. the fan of salsa is somewhere to the left of the fan of country##5
 9. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
10. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the right of the owner of the fish##5
11. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the person eating peach##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |    4     |
| Food          | peach     | cabbage   | orange | kale |
| Music-Genre   | disco | soul    | salsa   | country    |
| Pet           | fish       | ferret   | hedgehog   | chinchilla     |
| Transport     | subway       | roller | helicopter  | boat      |

