.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, hot-chocolate, coffee, water
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, sports, superhero, documentary
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, horse, lizard, ferret
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, tram, snowmobile
 1. the person watching superhero movies is on the far right##1
 2. the owner of the lizard is in an odd position##4
 3. the owner of the ferret is the person drinking lemonade##1
 4. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 5. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
 6. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person watching time-travel movies is between the person watching documentary movies and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
 8. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5
 9. the owner of the horse is the person watching documentary movies##1
10. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
11. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |      4       |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate       | lemonade | water     | coffee     |
| Movie-Genre   | sports      | time-travel       | documentary | superhero |
| Pet           | lizard       | ferret    | horse     | hedgehog         |
| Transport     | snowmobile | tram     | helicopter     | motorbike       |

