.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-3::.
There 4 different types of food: peach, watermelon, grapes, pineapple
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, animation, comedy, epic
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, indie, punk, salsa
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, goldfish, snake, rabbit
 1. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
 2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
 3. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the right of the fan of indie##5
 4. the fan of salsa is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rabbit##5
 5. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 6. the owner of the rabbit is between the fan of salsa and the fan of punk##2
 7. the fan of electronic is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goldfish##5
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is in an even position##4
10. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person eating peach##1
11. the person watching comedy movies is the owner of the hedgehog##1
12. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the left of the person eating grapes##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | pineapple    | grapes      | watermelon   | peach |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | comedy | animation | epic  |
| Music-Genre   | indie   | punk         | electronic  | salsa  |
| Pet           | snake      | hedgehog          | rabbit | goldfish  |

