.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, coffee, tea, milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, nurse, pilot, dancer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, d&b, folk, rock
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, parkour, badminton, snowboarding
 1. the fan of rock is somewhere to the left of the dressmaker##5
 2. the fan of rock is on the left of the dancer##1
 3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the pilot##3
 4. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
 5. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5
 6. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3
 7. the person drinking tea is between the fan of d&b and the person drinking milk##2
 8. the nurse is on the far left##1
 9. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3
10. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking coffee##5
11. the fan of folk is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
12. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##5
13. the fan of d&b is somewhere to the left of the dressmaker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |       3        |      4      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | coffee     | tea        | milk      |
| Job           | nurse    | dancer   | pilot | dressmaker |
| Music-Genre   | rock      | d&b    | classical        | folk         |
| Sport         | basketball    | badminton | snowboarding         | parkour    |

