The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, scientific, drama, family
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, pop, r&b, reggae
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, motorbike, snowmobile, van
 1. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is writing##5
 2. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 3. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##5
 4. the fan of punk is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 5. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the left of the person watching scientific movies##5
 6. the person driving the snowmobile is in an odd position##4
 7. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person driving the van##1
 8. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##5
 9. the person driving the van is the fan of r&b##1
10. the fan of pop is in an even position##4
11. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
12. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3       |      4       |
| Hobby         | collecting | reading    | dancing | writing  |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery  | scientific   | family       | drama |
| Music-Genre   | punk | pop        | reggae       | r&b      |
