There 4 different types of food: broccoli, strawberry, blueberry, radish
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, writer, bartender, nurse
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, indian, german, turkish
 1. the bartender is between the person drinking milk and the person eating radish##2
 2. the german is somewhere to the left of the person eating broccoli##5
 3. the indian is in an odd position##4
 4. the nurse is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5
 5. the person eating radish is the person drinking mirinda##1
 6. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person eating radish##1
 7. the person eating blueberry is on the left or right of the nurse##3
 8. the turkish is on the left or right of the writer##3
 9. the project-manager is somewhere to the right of the person eating blueberry##5
10. the person eating strawberry is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person eating strawberry is on the left or right of the german##3
12. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5
13. the turkish is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage      | milk             | hot-chocolate       | mirinda    | juice       |
| Food          | strawberry             | blueberry      | radish     | broccoli    |
| Job           | nurse | bartender | project-manager     | writer |
| Nationality   | indian           | german | turkish | mexican |

