10. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
11. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##5
12. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3
13. the person watching adventure movies is the person who's hobby is chess##1

