10. the social-worker is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
11. the person watching animation movies is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5
12. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3      |        4        |
| Beverage      | juice   | tea | fanta   | coffee          |
| Food          | cranberry    | carrot        | pear     | apple          |
| Job           | dancer | photographer        | social-worker | manager |
| Movie-Genre   | crime    | musical     | animation      | horror        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, 7up, lemonade, mirinda
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, social-worker, paramedic, teacher
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, action, satire, horror
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, tram, bike, train
 1. the person driving the tram is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
 3. the teacher is on the left or right of the police-officer##3
 4. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 5. the social-worker is between the paramedic and the person watching horror movies##2
 6. the person watching satire movies is in an odd position##4
 7. the paramedic is the person watching action movies##1
 8. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
 9. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
10. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the train##1
11. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
12. the person driving the train is on the right of the police-officer##1
13. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person watching satire movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | lemonade   | mirinda      | 7up | tea     |
| Job           | teacher   | police-officer  | social-worker        | paramedic |
| Movie-Genre   | family     | horror     | satire      | action   |
| Transport     | tram | bike | train          | van     |

