.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-20::.
There 4 different types of food: plum, garlic, mango, orange
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, electrician, writer, musician
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, adventure, mystery, superhero
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, r&b, d&b, funk
 1. the person eating mango is somewhere to the right of the person watching adventure movies##5
 2. the fan of funk is the person eating plum##1
 3. the person eating mango is somewhere to the left of the fan of folk##5
 4. the scientist is in an even position##4
 5. the electrician is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
 6. the fan of folk is somewhere to the right of the fan of r&b##5
 7. the writer is the person watching superhero movies##1
 8. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the left of the scientist##5
 9. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person eating plum##1
10. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating mango##5
11. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating orange##5
12. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere to the left of the person eating mango##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | plum | mango  | orange    | garlic       |
| Job           | electrician  | musician | writer | scientist  |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure    | mystery   | superhero  | western     |
| Music-Genre   | funk      | d&b    | r&b        | folk |

 